properties.Description:
*EFFECTIVE IMMEDIATELY*:
I-25 (northbound/southbound) from Interquest Parkway to Baptist Road:

properties.Name: NEW: Mandatory Evacuation A-1
properties.Description:
City officials have issued a Mandatory Evacuation Order effective immediately for the following area due to the Black Forest Fire.

Mandatory Evacuation Area A-1: Northern Boundary: North Gate and Old North Gate Road - Southern Boundary: Flying Horse Club Drive (to include homes south of Flying Horse Club Drive on Barossa Valley Road and Veneto Way)/Vine Cliff Heights/Equinox Drive/Serenity Peak Drive - Eastern Boundary: Highway 83 - Western Boundary: Voyager Parkway

properties.Name: 2:20 p.m.: Voluntary Evacuation Area A
properties.Description:
City officials have issued a Voluntary Evacuation Order effective immediately for the following area due to the Black Forest Fire.

Borders: West to I-25 and all areas north of Old Ranch Road within the City limits of Colorado Springs not included in Mandatory Evacuation Area A-1.

properties.Description: Norris Penrose Equestrian Center is FULL and no longer accepting large animals. Elbert County Fairgrounds and Flying W Ranch have space available.
